"Print version and exit.  Option B<-V> only works as B<--version> when it is "
"the only option."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.bfs.8:85
msgid ""
"The exit status returned by B<mkfs.bfs> is 0 when all went well, and 1 when "
"something went wrong."
