#. type: TH
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "MKFS.CRAMFS"
msgstr "MKFS.CRAMFS"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:32
msgid "mkfs.cramfs - make compressed ROM file system"
msgstr "mkfs.cramfs - 圧縮 ROM ファイルシステムの生成"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:35
msgid "B<mkfs.cramfs> [options] I<directory file>"
msgstr "B<mkfs.cramfs> [options] I<directory file>"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:38
msgid ""
"Files on cramfs file systems are zlib-compressed one page at a time to allow "
"random read access. The metadata is not compressed, but is expressed in a "
"terse representation that is more space-efficient than conventional file "
"systems."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:40
msgid ""
"The file system is intentionally read-only to simplify its design; random "
"write access for compressed files is difficult to implement. cramfs ships "
"with a utility (B<mkcramfs>(8)) to pack files into new cramfs images."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:42
msgid "File sizes are limited to less than 16 MB."
msgstr "ファイルシステムは 16 MB 未満に制限される。"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:44
msgid ""
"Maximum file system size is a little under 272 MB. (The last file on the "
"file system must begin before the 256 MB block, but can extend past it.)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:47
msgid ""
"The I<directory> is simply the root of the directory tree that we want to "
"generate a compressed filesystem out of."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:49
msgid ""
"The I<file> will contain the cram file system, which later can be mounted."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:57
msgid "B<-E>"
msgstr "B<-E>"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:59
msgid ""
"Treat all warnings as errors, which are reflected as command exit status."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:62
msgid "B<-b> I<blocksize>"
msgstr "B<-b> I<blocksize>"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:64
msgid "Use defined block size, which has to be divisible by page size."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:67
msgid "B<-e> I<edition>"
msgstr "B<-e> I<edition>"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:69
msgid "Use defined file system edition number in superblock."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:72
msgid "B<-N> I<big, little, host>"
msgstr "B<-N> I<big, little, host>"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:74
msgid "Use defined endianness. Value defaults to I<host>."
msgstr "指定されたエンディアンを使用する。 デフォルト値は I<host> である。"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:77
msgid "B<-i> I<file>"
msgstr "B<-i> I<file>"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:79
msgid "Insert a I<file> to cramfs file system."
msgstr "cramfs ファイルシステムに I<file> を挿入する。"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:82
msgid "B<-n> I<name>"
msgstr "B<-n> I<name>"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:84
msgid "Set name of the cramfs file system."
msgstr "cramfs ファイルシステム名を設定する。"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:87
msgid "B<-p>"
msgstr "B<-p>"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:89
msgid "Pad by 512 bytes for boot code."
msgstr "ブートコードとして 512 バイトを埋める。"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:94
msgid ""
"This option is ignored. Originally the B<-s> turned on directory entry "
"sorting."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:97
msgid "B<-z>"
msgstr "B<-z>"

#. type: Plain text
#: original/man8/mkfs.cramfs.8:99
msgid "Make explicit holes."
msgstr ""

